description:
This is a 9 minute workout called 'Instant Relaxation: 5-Minute Guided Breathwork for Nervous System Regulation' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: An easy 5 minute breathwork routine to help regulate your nervous system and calm anxiety.
